Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"A Shudder!\NThe Evil Hand Creeping Up on the Laboratory"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,D... Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Da...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around! Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Just come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You little punk! You gotta go back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you escape, we'll all get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But... I don't wanna go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go back! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--I can't take it anymore!\N--Just come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't ever wanna go back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! He doesn't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't get closer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Crying won't do any good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You shitty brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I can't take it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--Stop resisting!\N--Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--No!\N--You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--Screw that place!\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you kill me here?!\NEven if I go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I will die anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bartholomew Kuma is climbing the Red Line now\Nseemingly headed for Marijoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him enter Marijoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do,\Nit'll tarnish the Navy's reputation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad's past...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think I'll be able to face it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...with half-hearted determination.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I have to know it to be convinced!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Show it to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stella! Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how much damage they caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seraphim were all born here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but looks like they didn't hesitate at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee! I wonder what he's doing\Nat a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stella! Come on out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stella?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Was it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stella?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,An explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Respond! What was that explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Pythagoras?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pythagoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Something just exploded?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you okay, Luffy?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luffy! Can you hear me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is everything okay there?\NHas Vegapunk come back?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything is alright here,\Nbut Old Man Apple isn't back yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh please, where in the world did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Zoro there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's been here the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you keep an eye on him\Nso he doesn't wander off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't need another one getting lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, Old Man Ap...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--{\i1}What did you say? Say it again...{\i0}\N--It's happening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Luffy? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san? Please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Building C, Cam-snail 12,\Nscan the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find Pythagoras!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it an accident?\NI hope he wasn't caught in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cam-snail 12, search through the smoke!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A shadow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cam-snail has been destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nami! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you break it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go see Helmet for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:06.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,BUILDING C, BUILDING A, BUILDING B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:11.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,THIRD FLOOR, BUILDING A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Vegapunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, he's nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Respond if you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know where to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this place is pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If we play hide and seek here,\Nit'll never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?! Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! They're not what we're looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"They're jewels!" is\Nmost commonly followed by "Beautiful!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, isn't it?\NYou're all going to leave the island anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take them with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...is your common sense buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heavy so should we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to search for Stella!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overstuffing your bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll hardly be able to look for him\Nif you have that on your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}you{\i0} carry it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa-whoa-whoa-whoa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it here, so make sure\Nto lead us here on our way back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll come for you, my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, those are\Nman-made diamonds for industrial use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make diamonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with your eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The future is full of dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:13:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are crazy!\NStella! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's truly a facility that brings together\Nthe best of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You got beaten up by Lucci...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But was your face a mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:34.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,SECOND FLOOR, BUILDING A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can change your face and appearance\Nas you like! That's what the future is like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...Vegapunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an organoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an artificial organ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,An organoid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's technology\Nvital to the future of medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You can make organs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a stunning technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved. I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...this was a piece of\Na dismembered Vegapunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's too scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought\NI could go on a voyage with you one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You were at Mom's party, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You really pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I not notice\Nsuch a beautiful woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,From that moment, I've been your...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call me a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Get serious and look for Stella.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You silly boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Woof! Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a big laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you search every nook and cranny,\Nit'll take forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on a weapons-development floor,\Nso don't set off any shock waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:05.57,On Top,,0,0,0,,SECOND FLOOR,\NBUILDING B (ON THE RIGHT)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You be careful, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Helmet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Edison! This is Shaka! Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilith! York! Somebody! Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't contact anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,CONTROL ROOM,\NFOURTH FLOOR, BUILDING A
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hear them until a few minutes ago,\Nbut suddenly, I can't hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think I broke it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I really didn't!\NI didn't slam it into anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The video feeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...are going off one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Vegapunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,THIRD FLOOR,\NBUILDING C (ON THE LEFT)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep looking, York!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't leave soon,\Nthe Government will catch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Bubble Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A Bubble Gun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I can launch a very powerful\Nbubble attack that can deflect anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You say "deflect" but call it an attack?\NThat's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't imagine it,\Ndo you want a demonstration?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made by Vegapunk.\NIt must be an awesome weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're really interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,--What? What?\N--Did you find Stella?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!\NA big explosion must have taken place here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it an enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa-whoa-whoa, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's down on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pythagoras?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,His head is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His head was blown off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So this was the explosion we heard earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pythagoras! Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pythagoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,His head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Limbs are growing out of his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was gonna\Nget shot in the head as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Was it an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, judging from the situation,\Nwas it an enemy attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's inexplicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I don't think I was mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Just say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it an error in our design?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It really can't be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's York?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, Edison gave you an order to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be outside waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,York, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...I found this cutie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Love-Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...Mellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one!\NBoa Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the empress of Amazon Lily\Non the Island of Women,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the captain of the Kuja Pirates,\Nand one of the disbanded Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a Love-Love Fruit user\Nand can turn anyone she charms into stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She was born on September 2nd\Nand likes hot pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She is arrogant and selfish,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but behind it all is the trauma of having\Nonce been a slave of the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept the brand on her back secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but Luffy accidentally saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hancock was gonna kill Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but learning about his fearlessness\Nin beating up a Celestial Dragon openly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and witnessing his kindness and care,\Nshe fell in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call me Hancock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I got you, {\i1}Hammock{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At the request of her love, Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,she went to Impel Down\Nwhere Ace was being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Paramount War, despite being a Warlord,\Nshe apparently supported Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Seven Warlords system\Nwas abolished,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.46,0:23:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the Navy and the Blackbeard Pirates\Ncame to the Island of Women
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and a three-way battle erupted,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but with Dark King Rayleigh's help,\Nshe escaped the crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.92,0:23:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Seraphim suddenly launch\Nan attack on the Straw Hats.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They even ignore orders\Nfrom the Satellites.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is commanding them?{\i0}
